    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have absolutely got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one\u2014there's not a single blemish to be found, and it drives as smooth as silk. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
