    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 5.2L 'Voodoo' V8 featuring its signature flat-plane crankshaft and a stratospheric 8,250 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, equipped with the Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual and a 3.73 Torsen limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The MagneRide adaptive damping system and chassis bushings remain in showroom condition, ensuring zero lateral deflection under load. Braking performance is anchored by Brembo six-piston fixed front calipers with high-thermal capacity rotors, showing no signs of glazing or heat cycling. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle retains its factory-spec tolerances and peak compression across all cylinders. A turn-key powerhouse for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
