      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking example of automotive excellence, presented in a condition that can only be described as showroom-fresh. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains free of swirls, chips, or environmental imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a pristine sanctuary; the hand-stitched leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original factory scent. Every technological feature and mechanical component operates with the precision of a new vehicle. This car has been exclusively garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
